      "content": "fair enough, but if you look at the sheer scale of the changes in benefits vs the drop in participation, wouldn't you agree that the \"incentive\" argument is the most direct explanation? it feels like you're kind of downplaying the actual economic cost of these programs by focusing so much on the \"long term\" potential.",
